Key Features: 
    High Performance
        Support Embedded data models reduces IO activity
        Indexes support faster queries and can include keys from embedded docs and arrays
    Rich Query Language
        Read & Write
        Data Aggregation
        Text Search and Geospatial Queries
    High Availability
        replicaton
          automatic failover
          data redundancy
    Horizontal Scalability 
   
